headline: Oil Prices May Fall to $55 by 2026—Bad News for This Energy ETF
summary: After another lackluster year for the energy sector, 2026’s oil outlook spells trouble for the Big Oil stocks that constitute the XLE.

headline: 3 Oil Pipeline Stocks With Solid Potential Amid Industry Strength
summary: Midstream players will secure additional cashflows from rising clean energy demand from data centers, which brightens the outlook for the Zacks Oil and Gas - Production and Pipelines industry. Some of the frontrunners in the industry are EPD, KMI and WMB.
